parameters.name: DownloadKeyId
parameters.description: The ID of the download key, which is used to identify the parsing progress of data tracking logs. You can call the DownloadDataTrackResult operation to query the ID of the key.

parameters.name: OrderId
parameters.description: The ID of the ticket. You can call the [ListOrders](~~144643~~) operation to query the ID of the ticket.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The ID of the tenant. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](~~198073~~) or [ListUserTenants](~~198074~~) operation to query the ID of the tenant.
